BEGIN g-bbD204
CHAIN IF~RandomNum(7,1) ~THEN g-bbD204 g-bbD204.start
@0 /*You see a kuo-toa carrying a stack of boxes so tall that he is barely visible behind them. They look heavy, but the fish-man does not seem to mind. As you approach, he shakes with excitement and exclaims: "Lord Scar! I help. Good deed!" */
EXIT
CHAIN IF~RandomNum(7,2) ~THEN g-bbD204 g-bbD204.startq
@3 /*In front of you is a kuo-toa holding a basket of apples of dubious freshness. As soon as a resident of the Ditch settlement appears in the area, the fish-man gives them fruit, whether they want it or not. The kuo-toa smiles at you and nods eagerly. "Lord Scar! I help. Good deeds!" */
EXIT
CHAIN IF~RandomNum(7,3) ~THEN g-bbD204 g-bbD204.startw
@6 /*In front of you is a kuo-toa clutching a broom in his hand with such force as if it were at least a two-handed sword. He fiercely attacks the floor, sweeping dirt and dust into a pile. As you approach, the fish-man smacks his lips with excitement and bows before you. "Lord Scar! I help. Good deed!" */
EXIT
CHAIN IF~RandomNum(7,4)~THEN g-bbD204 g-bbD204.starte
@9 /*You see a kuo-toa holding a dirty rag in his hands. He is eagerly scrubbing the wall of a building. Admittedly, he is smearing dirt around rather than removing it, but the thought counts for something. When you approach him, he gives you a broad fishy smile. "Lord Scar! I help. Good deed!" */
EXIT
CHAIN IF~RandomNum(7,5) ~THEN g-bbD204 g-bbD204.startr
@12 /*You see a kuo-toa walking back and forth along the street, bending down occasionally to pick up some trash from the ground and put it in his mouth. He then chews it intensely, and swallows it with satisfaction. When you get closer, he waves his membranous paw at you in a friendly manner. "Lord Scar! I help. Good deed!" */
EXIT
CHAIN IF~RandomNum(7,6) ~THEN g-bbD204 g-bbD204.startt
@15 /*You see a kuo-toa kneeling on the street in front of you. He spits on the pavement every now and then, then scrubs it vigorously with a piece of rag. Several stones are already polished to a shine. When you get closer, the man-fish salutes you with a serious expression. "Lord Scar! I help. Good deed!" */
EXIT
CHAIN IF~RandomNum(7,7) ~THEN g-bbD204 g-bbD204.starty
@18 /*You see a kuo-toa standing in front of one of the buildings. He repeatedly runs his long tongue across the glass, bravely licking off the dirt. When you approach, he jumps up excitedly at the sight of you. "Lord Scar! I help. Good deed!" */
EXIT
CHAIN IF~RandomNum(7,0) ~THEN g-bbD204 g-bbD204.starto
@21 /*You see a kuo-toa sitting on the ground, holding a ginger cat on his lap. With surprising dexterity, his membranous hand picks fleas from the cat's fur and crushes them between his fingers. The animal seems to enjoy this, purring so loudly that it vibrates. As you approach, the fish-man nods his head respectfully in greeting. "Lord Scar! I help. Good deed!" */
EXIT